  The slab-based refactoring is complete. Key changes:
  - initialize(total_size_bytes, slab_size_bytes, ns_id) replaces the old
  (sizes, slots, ns_id) signature
  - Slabs are allocated dynamically on first create_extent for each size class,
  and auto-grow when full
  - SuperblockV2 with slab table (up to 256 entries), new magic EXTMGRV2
  - SlabDescriptor replaces SizeClassConfig; slab_index in ExtentMetadata for
  O(1) removal
  - Crash consistency preserved: zero slab blocks before superblock commit;
  two-phase record+bitmap writes unchanged

